title: Modify Traits to Accurately Reflect Artwork?
body:
Reasoning: Currently, artwork does not always match rarity. For example, the Astronaut Helmet overrides any masks that are listed in a Goober's traits. It is not possible to change the artwork, but we could modify traits to reflect the current artwork. This would remove traits from Goobers that don't actually display those traits.

Modifying these traits would affect the rarity ranking of all Goobers 
However, this change would ensure all Goobers accurately reflect their associated image.

Timeline: Trait modification would occur up to 1 week after the conclusion of this vote. 

Cost: There is no cost associated with this vote.
author: 0xcE1bb65eB4F7BCd2BB9DB3Cb982b524aB1Fa21a0
